data.name: ReadCaseRoleCase
data.value: select CAS_NUMBER, CSP_NUMBER, TYPE, CASE_ROLE_ID, END_DATE from CKT_CASE_ROLE where (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (END_DATE = @endDate) and (TYPE in ('AP', 'AR', 'CH')) order by CAS_NUMBER

data.name: ReadFips
data.value: select top(1) [STATE], COUNTY, LOCATION, STATE_DESC, COUNTY_DESC, LOCATION_DESC, STATE_ABBREVIATION, COUNTY_ABBR from CKT_FIPS where (COUNTY = cast(@count1 as integer)) and ([STATE] = cast(@count2 as integer))

data.name: ReadServiceProvider
data.value: select top(1) T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T1.USER_ID from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T1 join CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T2 on (T1.USER_ID = @userId) and (T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE > @effectiveDate) join CKT_ASSIGN_CASE T3 on (T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE = T3.OSP_DATE) and (T2.ROLE_CODE = T3.OSP_CODE) and (T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID = T3.OFF_ID) and (T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID = T3.SPD_ID) and (T3.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T3.DISCONTINUE_DATE > @effectiveDate) and (@casNo = T3.CAS_NO)
